00:11:32.360 --> 00:11:33.360
Tu cherches les ennuis ?

00:11:34.120 --> 00:11:35.840
Donc tu es Zhao Fengsheng.

00:11:37.320 --> 00:11:38.840
De toute ma vie...

00:11:38.919 --> 00:11:40.000
